"that we don't collide with local users uidNumber"
msgstr ""
"Na početku za uidNumbers, taj se broj dodaje user.pk kako bi se osiguralo da"
" brojevi nisu preniski za POSIX korisnike. Zadana postavka je 2000 kako "
"bismo osigurali da se ne sudaramo s lokalnim korisnicima uidNumber"

#: authentik/providers/ldap/models.py
msgid ""
"The start for gidNumbers, this number is added to a number generated from "
"the group.pk to make sure that the numbers aren't too low for POSIX groups. "
